org.sat4j.specs

インタフェース IGroupSolver

  • すべてのスーパーインタフェース:
    IProblem, ISolver, RandomAccessModel, java.io.Serializable
    既知のサブインタフェースのリスト:
    IGroupPBSolver
    既知の実装クラスのリスト:
    DimacsOutputSolver, DimacsStringSolver, GroupClauseSelectorSolver, GroupPBSelectorSolver, HighLevelXplain, LPStringSolver, OPBStringSolver, UserFriendlyPBStringSolver

    public interface IGroupSolver
extends ISolver
    Represents a CNF in which clauses are grouped into levels. It was first used to build a high level MUS solver for SAT 2011 competition.
    導入されたバージョン:
    2.3.3

    • メソッドの詳細

      • addClause

        IConstr addClause(IVecInt literals,
                  int groupId)
           throws ContradictionException
        パラメータ:
        literals - a clause
        groupId - the level of the clause set. The specific level 0 is used to denote hard clauses.
        戻り値:
        on object representing that clause in the solver.
        例外:
        ContradictionException
